                             'ezaMaze' V2.11

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'ezaMaze' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where you find yourself in a maze,
the idea is to find the exit in the least amount of moves. In each
game you play, the exit is at a different position... and not
necessarily at the edge of the labyrinth, in fact the exit can be
located at the center of the labyrinth...

  To complicate matters a little more, only a small portion of the
labyrinth, a 7 by 7 tile area, is shown. To help you, an arrow
indicates where the exit is located from your current position.

  You can choose the size of the labyrinth you want to play with.

  Have fun!

