@node features "Features"

                               Features

-Easy installation: just run the game and play!

-You can choose the size of the labyrinth. Any size between an
 area of 11 by 11 tiles up to an area of 59 by 59 tiles can be
 choosen.

-You can play the game (or change the size of the labyrinth) with
 the mouse or with the cursor keys of the keyboard.

-ezaMazeis a "Workbench" game, so it is meant to be played on the
 Workbench screen. The game window can be resized up to a maximum
 of 640 x 400 pixels, and the game is redisplayed according to the
 new window size. If the window is too small, it will automatically
 be resized to an adequate displayable size.

-A game you can play while waiting for other tasks to complete...
 or just for fun!

-As the game uses as little of the computer's ressources as
 possible, you can run other applications, games, etc. at the same
 time.

-ezaMaze works on all 68020(+) Amigas with Workbench 2.0 or
 higher.

@endnode

